title: Maruti Suzuki launches Swift S-CNG hatchback cars at an ex-showroom price of Rs 8.19 lakh
description: Maruti Suzuki's Indian subsidiary has launched the S-CNG variant of the Epic New Swift, boasting a fuel efficiency of 32.85 km/kg. The new model features a Z-series Dual VVT engine, available in three variants with enhanced safety and comfort features. Prices start at Rs 8.19 lakh ex-showroom.
